ness%20requirements%20and%20any%20technical%20limitations,%20as%20well%20as%20be%20responsible%20for%20conceiving%20and%20conducting%20user%20research,%20interviews%20and%20surveys,%20and%20translating%20them%20into%20sitemaps,%20user%20flows,%20customer%20journey%20maps,%20wireframes,%20mockups%20and%20prototypes.%3C/p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Senior%20UX%20Designer%20you%20will:%3C/p%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnderstand%20product%20specifications%20and%20user%20psychology%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETranslate%20concepts%20into%20user%20flows,%20wireframes,%20mockups%20and%20prototypes%20that%20lead%20to%20intuitive%20user%20experiences.%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFind%20creative%20ways%20to%20solve%20UX%20problems%20(e.g.%20usability,%20findability)%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConduct%20concept%20and%20usability%20testing%20and%20gather%20feedback%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDefine%20the%20right%20interaction%20model%20and%20evaluate%20its%20success%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDevelop%20personas%20through%20user%20research%20and%20data%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETake%20a%20user-centered%20design%20approach%20and%20rapidly%20test%20and%20iterate%20your%20designs.%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECommunicate%20design%20ideas%20and%20prototypes%20to%20developers%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIdentify%20design%20problems%20and%20devise%20elegant%20solutions.%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKeep%20abreast%20of%20competitor%20products%20and%20industry%20trends%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAsk%20smart%20questions,%20take%20risks%20and%20champion%20new%20ideas.%3C/li%3E%5Cn%3C/ul%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20id=%5C%22the-ideal-candidate%5C%22%3EThe%20Ideal%20Candidate%3C/h2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20a%20creative,%20outcome%20driven%20person,%20who%20knows%20that%20in%20a%20startup,%20your%20role%20often%20involves%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20responsibilities%20and%20change%20is%20a%20healthy%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20business.%3C/p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99re%20used%20to%20experimenting,%20with%20a%20Lean%20Build-Measure-Learn%20mentality%20who%20is%20not%20afraid%20test%20radic